  "$comment": "Canonical `kind` registry for the RAK OS Agentic Content Envelope (SPEC.md §3.1). Both the RAK content profile and the POXI/FOP market profile conform. Machine-readable source of truth for validators. Core is frozen; new capability = a new kind + ext validator, never a core migration.",
